{"type": "article", "id": 26905, "title": "可降解的公文包", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-17T06:45:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702152810BtUiHKZayWfeqjxX.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>为了应对环境污染，你或许已经见识过各种可降解的物品，来自德国的年轻品牌 <a href=\"http://www.rewrap.eu/\">reWrap</a> 想让你的日常用品也能带有环保属性，推出了这款用可降解材料制成的公文包。这个棕色的公文包主体由椰子纤维压制而成，缝线部分则使用了木浆。天然的材料以及简约的设计，看上去充满了大自然的气息。如果你感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"http://www.rewrap.eu/shop/tree-bag-large/\">链接</a>购买到这款足够环保的公文包，售价为 275 欧元（包含邮费）。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152807OfKArFG53hu8QTkx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152808ELAjXv4ZlNbiGWgf.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152808jVLyF8ElP0SCY7dX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152809EcTbN7FiyfUugs5B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71882641\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}